WEBVTT

00:00:02.135 --> 00:00:03.873
Big boys don't cry.

00:00:05.217 --> 00:00:06.404
Suck it up.

00:00:07.558 --> 00:00:09.232
Shut up and rub some dirt on it.

00:00:10.462 --> 00:00:13.136
Stop crying before I give you
something to cry about.

00:00:14.258 --> 00:00:16.116
These are just a few of the phrases

00:00:16.140 --> 00:00:19.314
that contribute
to a disease in our society,

00:00:19.338 --> 00:00:21.297
and more specifically, in our men.

00:00:22.595 --> 00:00:26.669
It's a disease that has come
to be known as "toxic masculinity."

00:00:28.044 --> 00:00:30.591
It's one I suffered a chronic case of,